\id 1TH - Dũya Translation Project
\h 1 Utasorhonika
\toc1 Ubvur Uburhu uwu inggbaashia aka atsɛnge abi Utasorhonika
\toc2 1 Utasorhonika
\toc3 1Uta
\mt2 Ubvur Uburhu uwu inggbaashia aka atsɛnge abi
\mt1 Utasorhonika
\imt1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur Utasorhonika uwu inggbaashia
\ip Uburhu uner itser Uyesu atsɛnge ubvur uwurɛ ra abika adɔsa ru Utasorhonika ra abĩ Umakidoniya. Abɔɔ agɛ Uburhu atsɛng ubvur uwurɛ ru Ukorinti ra amɛk aki 50-51 udzur ru unumkpi umbɔ aka amar Uyesu.
\ip Abika adɔsa ru Utasorhonika awu unying ra abika adɔsa ha Uburhu uner itser Uyesu aka adzin. Unga aka adzin umbɔ asi ikpoa inɛta umbɔ, ubinkutsu abi Uyahuda abee ifuw nggu unga na atsu unga abɔre umɔ (\xt Aiy 17.1-9\xt*). Uburhu atsɛng ubvur uwurɛ afituwe abika adɔsa ugɛ umbɔ adɛ̃ɛ̃ aker ri imangmangmbɔ.
\ip Ri inggbaashia, Uburhu atar uwɛɛ ru Unum ri itsi imangmangmbɔ nu ikikorhambɔ iyi ibibema nu ikɛi ifosayɛ umbɔ aka awerangge ru Ukiristo. Ubvur ha ufituwe abika adɔsa ugɛ umbɔ niba agbambɔ iwei ri itsi ibiba Ukiristo. Ikɛi udɛyiwe umbɔ ikpũ isiseiyɛ iki imɛ̃ umbɔ asei, na amina asumbɔ atɔ̃ itsermbɔ utsɛku Uyesu aka iba.
\iot Abinkɛ aka awe umɔ
\io1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur ha \ior (1.1-3)\ior*
\io1 Imangmang abi Utasorhonika \ior (1.4—3.13)\ior*
\io1 Ikpũ ibibɛkyɛ Unum aka abee \ior (4.1-12)\ior*
\io1 Imesa ri itsi ibiba Uteijee \ior (4.13—5.11)\ior*
\io1 Itsũwã iyi imaatak \ior (5.12-22)\ior*
\io1 Imimasha \ior (5.23-28)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ubvur uwurɛ udzeku umum Uburhu. Usirha nu Utimoti awu urhɔnga nggu umum umɛn ighwe umbi.
\p Ubvur uzĩ ri ikikɔng abika adɔsa ru Utasarhonika umbɔ aka awu abi Unum Utɛ nu Uteijee Uyesu Ukiristo.
\p Imimuta nu ididɔɔr ru umbi.
\s1 Itar uwɛɛ abi Utasorhonika ri imangmang
\p 
\v 2 Umɛn iki isaki itar uwɛɛ indzowe Unum ru umbi kishoo, iyisa atsokmbi ri ifɛn-Nummɛn.
\v 3 Umɛn idɛ̃ɛ̃ iyita ra asu Unum Utɛmɛn itsermbi iyi imangmang, nu ikikorhambi iyi ibibema, nu ibibimambi iyi ifosa ru Uteijeemɛn Uyesu Ukiristo.
\p 
\v 4 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umɛn ihwɛngmɛn awu Unum abema umbi na asɛng umbi,
\v 5 ubinkutsu, Isarhe Iyiki Izemɛn iba ru umbi isi iwengge ri irhɛm ukpekũ, bɔr iwe nggu ijee, nu Ipfu Isarsatangge nu ida icicang. Umbi ahwɛngmbi isiseimɛn iyi inggbaashia ru umbi umɛn iyika umbi.
\v 6 Umbi aka awu abika amesa umɛn nu Uteijee, ubinkutsu umbi ayɛi arherha ha ru nggaa ayetnum nggu anggɔmkɛ Ipfu Isarsatangge iki idzaa.
\v 7 Ngge itsu umbi awe abin aka amesa ra abika adɔsa kishoo ra abĩ Umakidoniya nu Uakaya.
\v 8 Asi iwea Umakidoniya nu Uakaya ukpekũ isarhe Uteijee iki idzeku umbi izĩ, bɔr imangmangmbi ru Unum aka ahwɛngmbɔ ubɛn anang. Nggee umɛn ishimɛn nu ubinkpi umɛn iki irherhe ra ake,
\v 9 ubinkutsu anera nibikambɔ aki isɔm ikpũ amɛnkɛ umbi aka akũ ayɛi umɛn. Umbɔ asɔm ugɛ umbi aka aneke idɔsa agberhe, na adzipa atɔ̃we itser ru Unum uwu idzidzɛrhe uwu urhɛ,
\v 10 na adzɛu Ungwɛ̃nga aka idzeka afã, uwuruwi unga aka azituwe ra akpe, Uyesu uwuku ushɔɔrte umɛn ru uvɔmwi uku iba.
\c 2
\s1 Itser Uburhu ru Utasorhonika
\p 
\v 1 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umbi ahwɛngmbi ugɛ iyiyepamɛn iki ĩba ru umbi isi igbangge abĩ.
\v 2 Umɛn iki ihwamɛn ayetnum nu urhena ru Ufirhipi, ru nyaka umbi aka ahwɛng, bɔr iyiyike Unummɛn itsu umɛn ĩdzaa umbi Isarhe Iyiki Izenga ra asu uver ukerketakpɔ ukpu ikpikpɛ̃ɛ̃.
\v 3 Ivangyɛ umɛn itsu umbi awe ru imangmang umɛn isi igbamɛn irhak use ida isisar use umɛn ibee ibvuta umbi.
\v 4 Bɔr umɛn iwu abirabɛ Unum aka anyã umɛn imɛ̃ɛ̃mɛn idzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize. Umɛn isi ĩbeemɛn irherhe abinkɛ anera aka abee bɔr abinkɛ Unum uwuku uvira amɛnmɛn aka abee.
\v 5 Umbi ahwɛngmbi arherhamɛn asi iweke itonga angwĩ, use umɛn ikũ ubin ukpɔɔ itsire atsimɛn ri ibee uhwɛk, Unum unga awu idekamɛn.
\v 6 Umɛn isi ĩbeemɛn anera akpoi umɛn, use umbi use abikase.
\p Umɛn iwu abi itser Uyesu umɛn iwemɛn ri ijee iyiki ibee ubin ru umbi,
\v 7 bɔr umɛn iwu ru nyaka awɛkaci ru umbi, ru nyaku uyi aki ikpɔm angwɛ̃nga.
\v 8 Umɛn ibema umbi akarhãrhã, ngge itsu umɛn isi ĩdzaamɛn umbi Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Unum ukpekũ, bɔr umɛn igũibɛn idzowe urhɛmɛn, ubinkutsu umbi awe azeze ru umɛn.
\v 9 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, idzidzɛrhe umbi ayitumbi ititɛ̃wãmɛn nu ayetnummɛn, umɛn itɔ̃ itser utsuu nu atenum isi igũmɛn azhe utsur umɛn iyɔmmɛn unera ru umbi ivangyɛ umɛn iki idzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize ru umbi.
\p 
\v 10 Umbi nggu Unum awu ideka, ra amɛn aka asar, nu irhirhika nu ida uvau umɛn iki iwe ru umbi abika adɔsa ri inggbaashia.
\v 11 Ubinkutsu umbi ahwɛngmbi umɛn iwe nggu umbi ru nyaka atei aki iwe nggu awɛkacimbɔ.
\v 12 Umɛn ifituwa ni iyika umbi ni itsu umbi asei ra amɛnkɛ Unum aka abee, unga aka ayisa umbi ri Iyɛrhanga nu ikpikpoi.
\p 
\v 13 Umɛn isi inekukumɛn itar uwɛɛ ru Unum ra akɛrɛ ha, ubinkutsu, ivangyɛ umbi aka ayɛi Arherhu-Num umbi aka agũ ru umɛn, umbi abema ake asi iweke ru nyaka arherhe anera, bɔr ru nyaka ake aka awe. Awe Arherhu-Num aka atɔ̃ itser ru umbi aka awe ru imangmang.
\v 14 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umbi awe abika amesu kishoo ikikɔng abika adɔsu Unum ru Uyahudiya, umbɔ aka awe ru Ukiristo Uyesu. Umbi ahwa ayetnum ra anermbi ubina unying nggu abika adɔsa ha aka ahwa ra abok abi Uyahuda,
\v 15 abika afɛre Uteijee Uyesu nu abika asɔm Arherhu-Num ikɛi na awayiwe umɛn idzek. Umbɔ adakuwe amɛn Unum na akpɛ̃mbɔ ubɛn unera
\v 16 ri ititɛ̃wãmbɔ umbɔ akɛnmbɔ umɛn idzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize ra atsen abi Uyahuda utsur umbɔ akpombɔ ififɔrh. Rimi hã ubɛn unum umbɔ aki itomu ugbiu arhimmbɔ akarhãrhã. Avɔm Unum aka acipuwake nu atsimbɔ.
\s1 Uburhu abee ibvui ayepa // abi Utasorhonika
\p 
\v 17 Bɔr umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, ivangyɛ umɛn iki idzipa ineke umbi ri ivanga ukunjiir, igigau ha iwu iyi iyor isi iwengge iyi amɛn, ngge itsu umɛn itsu asumɛn itɛ̃wã ibee ĩba inyã umbi.
\v 18 Ubinkutsu umɛn ibee ĩba ru umbi, udzumunga awu umum Uburhu iki ibee ikɛi nu ikɛi, bɔr Ushaitan akɛna umɛn.
\v 19 Asi iwea umbi awu ifosamɛn, nu igũibɛnmɛn nu ifur iyɛrheyɛ umɛn iki ikũ ifĩrhã ra asu Uteijee Uyesu unga aba abanga?
\v 20 Idzidzɛrhe umbi awu ikpikpoimɛn nu igũibɛn.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Nggee ivangyɛ umɛn iki ifɔr ibibima idamɛn, umɛn inyã izengge umbɔ aneka umɛn ukpekũ ru Uatina.
\v 2 Umɛn ĩdene Utimoti, aka awu ungwɛ̃mɛn nu uwɛrhu itser Unum ri idũwũ Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Ukiristo, unga adzaa umbi ikeramɛn na afituwa umbi ri imangmangmbi,
\v 3 ngge itsú unera asi ítsũwũka amɛnnga ri ivivira iyɛrɛ. Ubinkutsu umbi ahwɛngmbi ugɛ asɛng umɛn ikorha akɛrɛ ha.
\v 4 Idzidzɛrhe, ivangyɛ umɛn iki iwu nggu umbi, ubɛn unuma umɛn isɔma umbi ugɛ umɛn iwuri ihwa uver. Ngge iwe rimi hã, ru nyaka umbi aka ahwɛng.
\v 5 Ngge itsu, ivangyɛ umum iki isi idɛ̃ɛ̃ imɛ̃ɛ̃mum, umum ĩdene unga aba nu umum ima igũ isarhe imangmangmbi. Umum igũ iwei ugɛ use uwuku uvuviri ha aka avirunga umbi, ikɛi ayetnummɛn hã aka awe ibɛm.
\s1 Asɔm ififitu Utimoti
\p 
\v 6 Bɔr icɛrɛ Utimoti anai idzeku umbi aba ru umɛn, akũwã umɛn isarhe iyi imangmang nu ibibemambi. Unga asɔma umɛn ugɛ ubɛn unuma umbi anu iyita umɛn nggu iki ize na abee inyã umɛn, ru nyaka umɛn iki ibee inya umbi.
\v 7 Nggee, umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, ri kishoo igũ ighong nu uvermɛn, umɛn ikpomɛn ififita ri itsi imangmangmbi.
\v 8 Ubinkutsu, icɛrɛ umɛn iwemɛn ri ikeramɛn ikɛi, umbi aba adɛ̃ɛ̃ akermbi akarhãrhã ru Uteijee.
\v 9 Umɛn itarmɛn uwɛɛ ru Unum akarhãrhã ru umbi, ri igũibɛnyɛ umɛn iki iwurangge ra atsimbi ra asu Unummɛn.
\v 10 Nu utsuu nu atenum umɛn ifɛn-Num akarhãrhã ugɛ umɛn ima inyã umbi ikɛi ni ĩdzaa ubinkpi umbi aka ashimbi rakpɔ ri imangmangmbi.
\p 
\v 11 Unum Utɛmɛn itsikamnga nu Uteijeemɛn Uyesu ama ayanguwa utsĩndĩ uwuku uba ru umbi.
\v 12 Uteijee ha ama atomuwa ibibemambi ngge itɔk ni ibɔr igba ra adɔka nu ubɛn unera, ru nyaka umɛn iki ikorhuwa umbi.
\v 13 Unga ama atsu umbi awe ru ikeramɛn, ngge itsú umbi awe abika asheru uvau na awu asasar ra asu Unum Utɛmɛn, ivangyɛ Uteijeemɛn Uyesu aka iba nggu kishoo asarkasarnga.
\c 4
\s1 Isei isei iyiriyɛ Unum aka abema
\p 
\v 1 Ri imimasha, umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umɛn imesuwa umbi isei isei iyi ibibemu Unum, ru nyaka umbi aka asei. Icɛrɛ umɛn irhusa ni itsu umbi ri itsok Uteijee Uyesu àka atoma asei rimi hã.
\v 2 Ubinkutsu umbi ahwɛngmbi ubinkpi umɛn iki itsuka umbi ri ijee iyi Uteijee Uyesu.
\p 
\v 3 Awu ibibemu Unum umbi asei asasar, na niba akorhumbi kishoo itser itoma-dak.
\v 4 Ubɛn unera ru umbi amesi ikpɔm iyornga ru utsĩndĩ isisar nu imor,
\v 5 isi iwengge iyi ikponi iyor iyiriyɛ atsen abi Uyahuda aka asi ihwɛngmbɔ Unum.
\v 6 Ikɛi ra arherhe itoma-dak ha unera niba agbaa avau ru ungwɛ̃mbɔ use unga akpo utsĩndĩ adakuwe amɛn ungwɛ̃mbɔ. Uteijee awuri itsuka ufai ra anera ru ikpũ arhim akɛrɛ kishoo, ru nyaka umɛn iki isɔma umbi ni igbiita atombi.
\v 7 Ubinkutsu, Unum asi iyisunga umɛn isisei iyiki ida isisar, bɔr umɛn ibɛk ri isisar.
\v 8 Nggee, unga uwuku ukpɛ̃ imesa iyɛrɛ asi ikpɛ̃ɛ̃ unera, bɔr akpɛ̃ Unum, uwuku udzisa umbi Ipfunga Isarsatangge.
\p 
\v 9 Umɛn isi íbvui itsɛngamɛn umbi arherhe ibema angwɛ̃mbi, umbi nibikambi Unum aka amesuwanga umbi ibema adɔka.
\v 10 Idzidzɛrhe, umbi aka isaka abemumbi abika adɔsa kishoo ra abĩ Umakidoniya. Rimi hã umɛn ifituwa umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, àka atoma akorhe rimi hã ikɛi.
\p 
\v 11 Àka anyanga ngge iwu ubinkpi umbi aka abee, ri isei isei uku ughwɔɔw ri ibibɛkmbi, aka atsu amɛn ri itsermbi ukpekũ na akũ abokmbi atɔ̃ itser, ru nyaka umɛn iki isɔma umbi.
\v 12 Mɔcɛ inum ibibɛkmbi iwuri ikũ abirabɛ aka asi ihwɛngmbɔ Unum adzaa umbi imor, ngge itsú umbi aneke itsorha atsimbi ra ayor anera.
\s1 Ibiba Uteijee
\p 
\v 13 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umɛn isi ibeemɛn umbi awe abika ada ihwɛng ubin ri itsi abɔrɔ aka awu ru urhɔ akpe, use umbi agũ ighong ru nyaka aner abɔɔ, abika ashimbɔ ri ifosa.
\v 14 Umɛn iwemɛn ri imangmang ugɛ Uyesu akpe na asoka ikɛi, nggee umɛn iwemɛn ri imangmang ugɛ Unum awuri ikũ abika adɔsa ha aka akpe aba nggu Uyesu.
\v 15 Ru nyaka Arherhu Uteijee, umɛn idɛyiwa umbi ugɛ umɛn iki ibɛk icɛrɛ, umɛn ibɛk utsɛku ibiba Uteijee, umɛn isi ínggbaashia isomɛn ra abirabɛ aka awu ru urhɔ.
\v 16 Ubinkutsu Uteijee nibikanga awuri idzeka afã acipuwa, nggu uyisa ijee utsotsorakpɔ, nggu urhɛm unggbaashi ípfu itser-Num nu irhak utsom ukpu Unum, abika akpe ru Ukiristo awuri igbaashia asok.
\v 17 Aki ha aba amaake, umɛn abi urhɛ awuri ishupa umɛn nggu umbɔ ra amɛɛ ru umɛn ikpo Uteijee ra afafã. Nu umɛn iwuri iwe nggu Uteijee ugbagbaa.
\v 18 Nggee àka afituwe adɔka nggu irhɛm iyɛrɛ ha.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, ri itsi ivang nu inum, umɛn isi ibeemɛn itsɛnga umbi,
\v 2 ubinkutsu umbi ahwɛngmbi uku ushashaki ugɛ unum ukpu Uteijee uwuri iba ru nyaku uvɛu ru untsuuka.
\v 3 Ivangyɛ anera aka ani igɔr agɛ, <<Umɛn isei isei uku ughwɔɔw nu ififɔrh,>> kanying itsitsim iwuri ikpo umbɔ, ru nyaki ihwashi imar iki ikpo ukutsɛrh uwuku uwu ra anaa, utsĩndĩ ishishɔɔr ushimgbɔ ru umbɔ.
\p 
\v 4 Bɔr umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umbi asi iwembi ru uzĩ, ngge itsú unum hã usi ígbipukpɔ umbi ru nyaku uvɛu.
\v 5 Umbi kishoo awe angwɛ̃ irhirhang na angwɛ̃ atenum. Umɛn isi iwemɛn abi utsuu use abi uzĩ.
\v 6 Nggee, umɛn niba iwemɛn ru nyaka abɔɔ aka awe ru urhɔ, bɔr umɛn isei ĩdzɛu ni ikpɔm atsimɛn.
\v 7 Ubinkutsu abika arharhɔ arha ru untsuu nu abika afĩrhã adɛ afĩrhã ru untsuu.
\v 8 Bɔr umɛn iki iwe abi atenum, awu ufang umɛn ingwɛ̃dzɛn ni ikpɔm atsimɛn, itsim imangmang nu ibibema ru nyaka atorho uzɔu aki ikɔk, ni ifosi ififɔrh ru nyaki ifur uzɔu.
\v 9 Ubinkutsu, Unum asi itsũã umɛn ihwa ayetnum avɔmnga, bɔr atsũ umɛn ikpo ififɔrh ru ubok Uteijeemɛn Uyesu Ukiristo.
\v 10 Unga akpe ri itsimɛn, ngge itsú uko umɛn iwu aka arhi use umɛn iwu ru urhɔ, umɛn ima isei urhɔnga nggu unga.
\v 11 Nggee àka afita adɔka na adzin adɔka, ru nyaka umbi aki ikorhe.
\s1 Imimashi imesa
\p 
\v 12 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umɛn ishɔ̃rhã umbi, àka adzowe imor ra abika atɛ̃wũ itser ru umbi, anggbaashimbi ru Uteijee, abika adzaa umbi itsũwã.
\v 13 Àka akpɔm umbɔ afafã ri ibibema ri itsi itsermbɔ. Àka asei uku ughwɔɔw nggu adɔka.
\v 14 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn, umɛn ishɔ̃rhã umbi, àka agbiite ato abi ighɛrha ru umbi, àka afituwe abika asheri ikeramɛn ru umbi, àka ayike abika asheri iker ru umbi, àka adɔng amɛnmbi nggu ubɛn unera.
\v 15 Àka angwɛ̃dzɛn, utsur unera afasa iyiki ibewe nggu iyiki ibewe, bɔr ubɛn ivang àka akorhi iyiki ize nggu adɔka nu ubɛn unera.
\p 
\v 16 Àka agɔm anggɔm ubɛn ivang,
\v 17 àka niba anekukumbi ifɛn-Num,
\v 18 àka atar uwɛɛ ri kishoo ubinkpi uku uwe, ubinkutsu ngge iwu ibibemu Unum ru umbi ru Ukiristo Uyesu.
\p 
\v 19 Àka niba arhĩwukumbi Ipfu-Num.
\v 20 Àka niba akwɛɛrkumbi itser iyiki isɔm Arherhu-Num,
\v 21 àka avira abina kishoo, na akpɔm akirakɛ aka awe aka aze,
\v 22 àka atĩmbi ubɛn iyiki ibewe.
\p 
\v 23 Unum nibikanga, Unum uwu ididɔɔr, ama asare umbi undzumunga, ipfumbi nu urhɛmbi nu ayormbi kishoo ima isheru uvau ru unumkpi Uteijeemɛn Uyesu Ukiristo aka iba.
\v 24 Unga awuri ikorhunga ake, ubinkutsu unga uwuku uyisa umbi awu uner idzidzɛrhe.
\p 
\v 25 Umbi angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn àka afɛna-Num ru umɛn.
\v 26 Àka aghwe adɔka nggu ighwe ibibema.
\v 27 Umum ishɔ̃rhã umbi ri itsok Uteijee, àka avarhuwe ubvur uwurɛ ra angwɛ̃mɛn nu anapumɛn kishoo.
\p 
\v 28 Imimuta Uteijeemɛn Uyesu Ukiristo ima iwe nggu umbi.
